  "title": "Staff Nurse (Endoscopy, Entry Level) - Travel is required",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist the doctor during endoscopic and surgical procedures (both minor and major).</li>\n  <li>Perform wound care and dressing changes.</li>\n  <li>Manage and organize daily clinic operations to ensure smooth workflow.</li>\n  <li>Schedule and coordinate patient appointments efficiently.</li>\n  <li>Handle billing, payment collection, and basic administrative tasks.</li>\n  <li>Perform any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/ Degree in Nursing</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid SNB</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates are welcome, training is provided.</li>\n  <li>Must be comfortable to travel around the clinics islandwide.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
